---
title: HelloHero: Caribbean Beef & Slaw Tacos with Pineapple & Peanuts
description:  A dinner time fave, is being whipped up tonight. Beef tacos that are glazed and topped with juicy and sweet pineapple. Go crazy and add a sprinkling of peanuts to enjoy these amazing tacos.

